416
00:30:50,486 --> 00:30:52,237
<b>Hai, sayang.</b>

417
00:30:52,696 --> 00:30:53,822
<b>"Sayang"?</b>

418
00:30:54,490 --> 00:30:56,116
<b>Siapa perempuan itu?</b>

419
00:30:56,867 --> 00:30:59,077
<b>Tiada sesiapa. Jangan risau. 
Tumpukan perhatian pada penulisan awak.</b>

420
00:31:01,413 --> 00:31:02,456
<b>Tak guna.</b>

421
00:31:03,749 --> 00:31:05,334
<b>Kedengarannya seperti gadis muda.</b>

422
00:31:07,294 --> 00:31:08,545
<b>Dimana saya?</b>

423
00:31:12,216 --> 00:31:15,511
<b>Ini adalah Hospital Psikiatri OK, 
